title: Beatriz' War (2014)
description:
First feature film produced in the young country of Timor-Leste.
Although a fictional account, it depicts situations that many in Timor faced during the bloody 24 year occupation.

The film is in Tetum, one of the main languages spoken in Timor - with English subtitles.

If you like the film, please consider purchasing a copy to encourage filmmaking in Timor.
